                "collapsible_apEYAY": {
                  "type": "collapsible",
                  "name": "Collapsible",
                  "settings": {
                    "label": "What makes your brand different than other supplements?",
                    "metafield_namespace_key": "",
                    "metafield_image_key": "image",
                    "metafield_label_key": "title",
                    "accordion_class": "accordion",
                    "content": "<p>Our supplements are designed for significantly improved absorption using advanced delivery technologies that help nutrients enter your system more effectively. Unlike many traditional supplements where a large portion isn’t absorbed, our formulations use proprietary methods like nanoparticle technology and liposomes to enhance bioavailability, helping you get more benefit from every dose.</p>",
