                    "content": "<p>We uniquely formulate each supplement using a combination of absorption-enhancing technologies, such as liposomes and advanced nano-delivery systems. We don’t rely on a single method. Instead, we select and layer multiple techniques based on the specific ingredient and how the body best absorbs it.This approach allows us to create pharmaceutical-grade supplements designed for significantly improved bioavailability, delivering up to 149× better absorption.</p>",
